nature and variety of work
the office of management and budget (omb) is currently seeking highly qualified individuals to fill a vacant budget management analyst i/ii position, grade g18/21.

this is entry-level to full performance professional work involving all phases of budgetary development, administration, and management analysis projects for assigned county departments and agencies. incumbents collect, tabulate and analyze budgetary, management, statistical and accounting data and prepare associated written analysis and reports. work is performed under the close supervision of a higher-level supervisor.
